		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Wondrous Item - Rare</em></p><p>This necklace has 1d6 + 3 beads hanging from it.</p><p><strong>Action</strong> - 60 ft.</p><ul><li><p>When it reaches the end of its trajectory, the bead detonates as a level 3 <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.pbT9cw6nsjpmwrVZ]{Fireball}</em> (save DC 15).</p></li><li><p>You can hurl multiple beads, or even the whole necklace, at one time. When you do so, increase the damage of the <em>Fireball</em> by 1d6 for each bead after the first (maximum [[/damage 12d6 fire]]).</p></li></ul><section class=\"secret\" id=\"foundry-secret-1\"><p><strong>Foundry Note</strong></p><p>This item includes 9 limited uses. The <strong>Determine Number of Beads</strong> activity can be used to determine how many beads (equivalent to 1d6 + 3) are on the necklace.</p><p>The <strong>Throw Bead</strong> activity allows you to scale the Fireball up to a max of 12d6.</p></section>",
